                <p rend="sectiontitleital">REPRESENTATION BY GRADE LEVEL</p>
                <p>As indicated in the report to the President, we believe the level of jobs held by
                    women and minorities to be a better measure of their advancement (and therefore
                    of the effectiveness of affirmative action efforts) than overall representation.
                    For your agency, these representation levels are as follows:</p>
