                <p rend="sectiontitleital">NON-CAREER EXECUTIVE APPOINTMENTS</p>
                <p>Of special interest is your agency’s performance in hiring non-career executives.
                    Non-career executives are employees at grades <gloss target="#t_GS_1">GS</gloss>
                    16–18 with Non-career Executive Assignments. Included are also a few employees
                    at these levels with Schedule C appointments and a small number with
                    Presidential appointments, with the advice and consent of the Senate.</p>
                <p>For these employees, you show the following picture:</p>
